<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="1" type="reference_group">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
<taxonomicName authorityName="Steyskal" authorityYear="1980" class="Insecta" family="Phytomyzinae" genus="Haplopeodes" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Haplopeodes" order="Diptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Haplopeodes</taxonomicName>
Steyskal, 1980: 141. Type species: 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Meigen" baseAuthorityYear="1838" class="Insecta" family="Phytomyzinae" genus="Phytomyza" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Phytomyza minuta" order="Diptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="minuta">Phytomyza minuta</taxonomicName>
<bibRefCitation author="Frost, SW" journalOrPublisher="Memoir of the Cornell Agricultural Experiment Station" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" pagination="1 - 228" refId="B75" refString="Frost, SW, 1924. A study of the leaf-mining Diptera of North America. Memoir of the Cornell Agricultural Experiment Station 78: 1 - 228" title="A study of the leaf-mining Diptera of North America." volume="78" year="1924">Frost 1924</bibRefCitation>
: 86, by original designation. 
<bibRefCitation author="Spencer, KA" journalOrPublisher="Agriculture Handbook" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" pagination="1 - 478" publicationUrl="https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/page/51258090" refId="B261" refString="Spencer, KA, Steyskal, GC, 1986b. Manual of the Agromyzidae (Diptera) of the United States. U.S.D.A. Agriculture Handbook 638: 1 - 478, https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/page/51258090" title="Manual of the Agromyzidae (Diptera) of the United States. U. S. D. A." url="https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/page/51258090" volume="638" year="1986 b">Spencer and Steyskal 1986b</bibRefCitation>
